			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I have been looking at my training point surplus (I have spent 4 or 5 so far) and at the skills I need to train. I don't see any skills that demand saving a whole bunch.
<br />

<br />
I am thinking of burning a whole bunch on throwing and later intimidation (which seem to be the hardest to bring up through practice).
<br />

<br />
Is this a good plan or are there better things to spend the points (and plat) on?</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
